_025_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28462,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱلْمُنِيرِ","translation":"দীপ্তিময়","audioUrl":"wbw/035_025_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28463,"position":14,"arabic":"٢٥","translation":"(২৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":26,"arabic":"ثُمَّ أَخَذْتُ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ ۖ فَكَيْفَ كَانَ نَكِيرِ","translation":"[but] in the end I took to task all those who were bent on denying the truth: and how awesome was My rejection!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3686.mp3","surahId":35,"words":[{"id":29363,"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/035_026_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29364,"position":2,"arabic":"أَخَذْتُ","translation":"আমি পাকড়াও করেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/035_026_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29365,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"তাদেরকে (যারা)","audioUrl":"wbw/035_026_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29366,"position":4,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟ ۖ","translation":"অস্বীকার করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_026_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29368,"position":5,"arabic":"فَكَيْفَ","translation":"অতঃপর কেমন (দেখো)","audioUrl":"wbw/035_026_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29369,"position":6,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/035_026_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29370,"position":7,"arabic":"نَكِيرِ","translation":"আমার শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/035_026_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29371,"position":8,"arabic":"٢٦","translation":"(২৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":27,"arabic":"أَلَمْ تَرَ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ أَنزَلَ مِنَ ٱلسَّمَآءِ مَآءًۭ فَأَخْرَجْنَا بِهِۦ ثَمَرَٰتٍۢ مُّخْتَلِفًا أَلْوَٰنُهَا ۚ وَمِنَ ٱلْجِبَالِ جُدَدٌۢ بِيضٌۭ وَحُمْرٌۭ مُّخْتَلِفٌ أَلْوَٰنُهَا وَغَرَابِيبُ سُودٌۭ","translation":"ART THOU NOT aware that God sends down water from the skies, whereby We bring forth fruits of many hues - just as in the mountains there are streaks of white and red of various 